high_descs: Turn around, go to wall, turn right to face counter.
Pick up pump bottle furthest to the left, closest to the wall.
Turn right, proceed to end of sink area, turn left.
Put pump bottle on back of toilet, to left of candle.
anns.task_desc: Move pump bottle to back of toilet.

high_descs: Turn left towards the sink, turn left towards the wall, and then turn right to face the lotion bottles on the counter.
Pick up the lotion front lotion bottle closest to the wall.
Turn right and walk towards the toilet.
Place the bottle on the left side of the toilet basin.
anns.task_desc: Place the bottle from the sink counter on the toilet basin.

high_descs: Walk to the left of the kitchen sink.
Grab one of the bottles with the green tops.
Go to the toilet on the right.
Place the bottle on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle from the sink to the toilet.
